OL,3,CDrink driver jailed after high-speed
OL,4,Cchase in Leicester
OL,6,FA drink-driver hit high speeds while
OL,7,Fbeing pursued by police in Leicester.
OL,9,FDuring a period of 22 minutes, Jason
OL,10,FMongan overtook cars on solid white
OL,11,Flines approaching oncoming traffic,
OL,12,Fdrove on the wrong side of the road
OL,13,Fand also went through a red light.
OL,15,FAt one point, the 30-year-old also
OL,16,Fdrove at 80mph in a 40mph area.
OL,18,FMongan was sentenced at Leicester
OL,19,FCrown Court on Friday, 15 November.
