OL,6,FPC Stephen Bates, who was the pursing
OL,7,Fofficer, said: "Mongan's actions that
OL,8,Fday could have resulted in serious
OL,9,Finjury, or even a fatality.
OL,11,F"The fact that no other road user, or
OL,12,FMongan himself, was injured that
OL,13,Fafternoon was very fortunate.
OL,15,F"Thankfully his driving was captured
OL,16,Fon dash camera and the NPAS camera,
OL,17,Fwhich provided crucial evidence in
OL,18,Fcourt, and I am relieved that he has
OL,19,Faccepted responsibility for his
OL,20,Factions that day."
