OL,3,CDrink driver jailed after high-speed
OL,4,Cchase in Leicester
OL,6,FPolice said at around 1.30pm on
OL,7,FSunday, 28 January this year, an
OL,8,Fofficer witnessed a grey Peugeot 5008
OL,9,Fdriving along New Parks Way, Leicester
OL,10,Fand requested the driver to stop with
OL,11,Fhis blue lights.
OL,13,FThe driver failed to stop and a
OL,14,Fpursuit was authorised.
OL,16,FAn aircraft from National Police Air
OL,17,FService also assisted tracking the
OL,18,Fvehicle, as it continued ignoring the
OL,19,Fofficers in pursuit.
