OL,3,CDrink driver jailed after high-speed
OL,4,Cchase in Leicester
OL,6,FThe pursuit ended after the car came
OL,7,Fto stop in a car park in Ullesthorpe
OL,8,Fand the driver, identified as Mongan,
OL,9,Fwas arrested on suspicion of failing
OL,10,Fto stop and dangerous driving.
OL,12,FA roadside breath test was carried out
OL,13,Fand Mongan blew 72 ` more than twice
OL,14,Fover the legal limit ` so he was also
OL,15,Farrested on suspicion of drink
OL,16,Fdriving. He then provided specimens of
OL,17,F57 and 61 in police custody.
