OL,3,CDrink driver jailed after high-speed
OL,4,Cchase in Leicester
OL,6,FHe was later charged with failing to
OL,7,Fstop, dangerous driving and driving a
OL,8,Fvehicle when alcohol level was above
OL,9,Fthe limit and pleaded guilty to all
OL,10,Foffences at court in August.
OL,12,FMongan, of Mere Road, Bitteswell,
OL,13,FLutterworth was sentenced to 12 months
OL,14,Fin prison. He was also disqualified
OL,15,Ffrom driving for 30 months and ordered
OL,16,Fto carry out an extended re-test.
